    "Footnote 8 (Continued) into groups.",
    "10 AI is beset by the idea that the brain does the work of making knowledge whereas most of what the brain does is extract knowledge from the groups in which it is embedded.",
    "This is another way of expressing the basic insight of the sociology of knowledge.",
    "The dominant mode of artificial intelligence work up until the last ten years or so was what was known disparagingly by its critics as 'good old-fashioned AI' or GOFAI.",
    "It involved humans writing programs meant to reproduce human thinking."
